{
  "stem": "2916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they made a pile of it, and they put it to the torch, books, documents, certificates, pictures, every picture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's the reason why I don't have any pictures.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had asked me to find and display some pictures from our life before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But everything had to be handed over, and then it was put to the torch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All the men who had beards had to shave it off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some men had ear locks, the traditional peyos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Jewish peyos, had to be shaven off, so that we were prepare for deportation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then from this place, we were deported to another town, a larger town, another ghetto, as they called it, which was just the synagogue itself.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody was crowded into the synagogue of this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "By that time, we were told we were between 4,000 to 5,000 people in the synagogue building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you can imagine the crowding was just unbearable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All you had was you could spread a blanket and each family lived on that blanket, and next to you another family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the-- among these circumstances, we were for a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During this time, many people died, I imagine that people who were prone to heart attacks, elderly, and probably the fear and the crowding.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were many deaths.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the first time that I sort of experienced close hand death, because people died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when the trains came, when the news reached us that the cattle cars came and we will be taken away from here, people were happy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we thought that this was unbearable and-- and anything else would be better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we-- a week later we were loaded onto trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't a regular passenger train.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
